       <h2>
        Welcome from the Chair, Pamela Radcliff
       </h2>
       <p>
        <a href="people/office-hours.html">
        </a>
        As Chair, I would like to welcome you to the Department of History at UC San Diego. Comprised of 40 full-time
        <g class="gr_ gr_15 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar multiReplace" data-gr-id="15" id="15">
         <g class="gr_ gr_15 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar multiReplace" data-gr-id="15" id="15">
          faculty
         </g>
        </g>
        , we offer excellent undergraduate and graduate programs in a number of geographic and thematic areas. Our faculty
        <g class="gr_ gr_17 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar multiReplace" data-gr-id="17" id="17">
         <g class="gr_ gr_17 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar multiReplace" data-gr-id="17" id="17">
          have
         </g>
        </g>
        earned national and international recognition for their scholarship as well for teaching.
        <strong>
         <a href="about/chairs-welcome.html">
          Read More
         </a>
        </strong>
       </p>
       <hr/>
       <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
         <p>
          Your donations directly support the History Department.
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col">
         <h3 style="text-align: justify;">
          <a href="http://www-er.ucsd.edu/givetoucsd/secure/paymenttran/onlinegiving.asp?sk=3&amp;txtFundName=Department%20of%20History%20Fund%20(2365)&amp;txtFundNo=2365&amp;txtSolicCode=&amp;pk=">
           <img alt="Give to the History Department" height="34" src="_images/give-now.png" width="114"/>
          </a>
         </h3>
        </div>
       </div>
       <hr/>
       <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
         <p>
          Meet with one of our faculty by making an appointment or stopping by during their regular office hours.
         </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col">
         <a href="people/office-hours.html">
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" type="button">
           Faculty Office Hours
          </button>
         </a>
        </div>
       </div>
